rows.label: tlk43310191_01_msg0001
rows.name:
War with Superbia could easily
break out at any time.

rows.label: tlk43310191_01_msg0002
rows.name:
That's why we're stocking up the
Divine Beast battleship with food rations.

rows.label: tlk43310191_01_msg0003
rows.name:
If the Empire make a move to expand
their territory, only Invidia will be able
to stop them!

rows.label: tlk43310191_01_msg0004
rows.name:
So we must always be on our guard,
for the sake of other nations as well.
